dct_title_s: Denmark = Dänemark = Danemark = Dinamarca = Danii︠a︡ / Reise Know-How.
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by gradient tints and spot heights. Depths shown by bathymetric tints. "Projek.: Lambert conformal. Ellipsoid: WGS84. UTM: Zone 32/33." "Exact elevation lines, high-altitude relief, GPS-compatible, with gradation network & UTM grid, classified street network, detailed local index." --Translated from back panel. 2 insets: Bornholm -- Hesselø. Includes location map, illustrations. Title from panel. "Rip & waterproof." Map is continued on verso.
